"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US Central Command says that strikes on Iranian missile launch sites and boats were done in self-defense. The US secretary of state mentioned that an agreement might be reached on Monday. Trump also mentioned that an agreement would include reopening the Strait of Hormuz.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Strikes in Self-Defense\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Comando Central de EE.UU. dice que los ataques a sitios de misiles y barcos iran\u00edes fueron en defensa propia. El secretario de estado de EE.UU. mencion\u00f3 que un acuerdo podr\u00eda alcanzarse el lunes. Trump tambi\u00e9n mencion\u00f3 que un acuerdo incluir\u00eda reabrir el Estrecho de Ormuz.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques de EE.UU. en Defensa Propia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Ukrainian capital experienced one of the largest aerial attacks of the war overnight on Saturday. This comes as tensions continue to rise in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Large Aerial Attack in Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"La capital de Ucrania sufri\u00f3 uno de los mayores ataques a\u00e9reos de la guerra durante la noche del s\u00e1bado. Esto ocurre mientras las tensiones siguen aumentando en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gran Ataque A\u00e9reo en Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military has targeted areas in eastern Lebanon after the prime minister announced more strikes. This is part of ongoing conflicts in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Strikes in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed ha atacado \u00e1reas en el este del L\u00edbano despu\u00e9s de que el primer ministro anunciara m\u00e1s ataques. Esto es parte de los conflictos en curso en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques Israel\u00edes en L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kem Sokha was sentenced to 27 years on charges of treason, which many believe were politically motivated. His case has drawn international attention and criticism.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kem Sokha Sentenced\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kem Sokha fue sentenciado a 27 a\u00f1os por cargos de traici\u00f3n, que muchos creen que fueron motivados pol\u00edticamente. Su caso ha atra\u00eddo atenci\u00f3n y cr\u00edticas internacionales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Kem Sokha Sentenciado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Saudi Arabia reports that 11,000 more Muslims traveled to the Gulf kingdom this year compared to last year. This increase is significant for the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Increase in Muslim Travelers to Saudi Arabia\",            \"translated_version\": \"Arabia Saudita informa que 11,000 musulmanes m\u00e1s viajaron al reino del Golfo este a\u00f1o en comparaci\u00f3n con el a\u00f1o pasado. Este aumento es significativo para la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Aumento de Viajeros Musulmanes a Arabia Saudita\"        }    ]}"